		<title>GreenInked, repenser l’habitat et le développement durable (2/2)</title>
		<link>http://www.al-kanz.org/2008/12/09/greeninked-developpement-durable/</link>
		<comments>http://www.al-kanz.org/2008/12/09/greeninked-developpement-durable/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 09 Dec 2008 11:56:21 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Al-Kanz</dc:creator>
		
